<p>This is right up there with tires being toxic when used for earthships or landscape timbers making gardens toxic.  Seems like it makes sense on the surface, lots of folks saying it is true but no proof and doesn&#8217;t really pass the test if you know a bit more then &#8220;tires are dirty&#8221; or &#8220;cars have exhaust pipes&#8221;.</p>
