<p>Atheist &#8211; a person who denies or disbelieves the existence of a supreme being or beings</p>
<p>Agnostic &#8211; One who believes that it is impossible to know whether there is a God. or one who is skeptical about the existence of God but does not profess true atheism</p>
<p>Those are text book definitions, if you insist on labeling yourself choose wisely don&#8217;t expect others to modify the definition on your behalf.  Again I don&#8217;t care what you believe but when you tell me or most people you are atheist or agnostic, we are going to assume you know the definition of the word you use to define yourself.   </p>
